(59, 1, '2020-10-13 17:22:38', '2020-10-13 09:22:38', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>ツナパハ(不思議香菜TUNAPAHA)</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:gallery {\"ids\":[70]} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wb/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/20190910_133734-1-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"不思議香菜TUNAPAHA-drycurry\" data-id=\"70\" data-full-url=\"http://localhost/wb/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/20190910_133734-1-scaled-e1602750513731.jpg\" data-link=\"http://localhost/wb/20190910_133734-1/\" class=\"wp-image-70\"/></figure></li></ul></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TUNAPAHA獨特的香料與辣味，讓許多福岡人傾心於它。日本很多店家都有所謂的午餐特惠時間，在這段時間會有比平常餐點更為便宜的午餐價格，而TUNAPAHA到下午五點都還是午餐特惠時間，這也是它人氣居高不下的原因之一。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>由斯里蘭卡的主廚研發適合日本人的辣味料理，搭配椰汁的甜味，讓辣味添加了不同層次的風味。或者您也可以嘗試附上檸檬的ドライカリー(dry curry)，酸與辣的結合是這道料理的精華之處。</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d512.2246261380157!2d130.39652243688573!3d33.588628726010604!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3541918609df122f%3A0xd6a29327ae713b96!2sTunapaha!5e0!3m2!1szh-TW!2sjp!4v1602757437907!5m2!1szh-TW!2sjp\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" aria-hidden=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"></iframe>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', '在當地人心中人氣居高不下的斯里蘭卡咖哩。', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e6%a8%99%e9%a1%8c%e4%b9%9d', '', '', '2020-10-26 15:12:48', '2020-10-26 07:12:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wb/?p=59', 0, 'post', '', 0),
